short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: To enable sales professionals on Hubspot to identify the psychological profile of their prospects

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
BusinessBlots, an extension of the BrandBlots platform by Inkblot Analytics, allows sales professionals on Hubspot to identify the psychological profile of prospects and get recommendations on how to interact with them on different mediums (e.g. calls, emails, meetings, etc.).

Can only be used with access to Hubspot.
